Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們屍鬼 以人為食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:05.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到夏野死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:10.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節子和幹康也是那副樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:14.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到討厭的傢伙遭罪 真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:19.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:22.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:23.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:47.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:53.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
