Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.26,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.26,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代價
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.33,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.33,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:39.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}連這淚水都能將之奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.41,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命は脆くて儚くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:42.41,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飄忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.88,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:45.88,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}當一切造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.21,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.21,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.21,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要將死亡歎作恐怖嗎
